LinuxPromotion LiveCD Source
===========================
The LiveCD created to help people get used to linux while lowering the learning curve
needed for learning Linux. Created for the Linux Promotion project.

http://linuxpromotion.org

Building
=======
How to build:
0. Get the repo.
git clone https://github.com/soccermitchy/lp-live.git
cd lp-live

1. Ensure your build setup is clean.
sudo lb clean
sudo rm -rf cache/

2. Build the distro.
sudo lb build

3. Test the distro
kvm -cdrom *.hybrid.iso
